name: CNN
text:
Drug giant AstraZeneca said it had paused global trials of its Covid-19 vaccine because of an unexplained illness in one of the volunteers.

It's a standard precaution in vaccine trials, meant to ensure experimental vaccines don't cause serious reactions. https://t.co/DLevrm1TZc
